796
00:55:30,461 --> 00:55:32,583
(Mi novio es tan lindo.)

797
00:55:39,789 --> 00:55:42,083
Oh. Je.

798
00:55:46,231 --> 00:55:48,736
Feliz primer mes de aniversario, Krit.

799
